---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/about.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="Meet Antonio" description="Meet Antonio, your Amazon guide, and discover how Águia Amazonas works with the local community to create authentic journeys.">
  <section class="page-hero wrap">
    <div><p class="eyebrow">Rooted here</p><h1>The Amazon<br/>is personal.</h1></div>
    <p>Águia Amazonas is Antonio, your guide to the Amazon. He works closely with the local community to offer authentic, respectful experiences shaped by a lifetime of local knowledge.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="story-grid wrap">
    <div class="story-image"><img src="/images/people/antonio.webp" alt="Antonio, founder and guide at Águia Amazonas" /><span>Antonio<br/>Founder · Guide · Host</span></div>
    <div class="story-copy"><p class="eyebrow light">Meet your host</p><h2>Welcome to my home.</h2><p>“Welcome to Brazil and the Amazon rainforest—my home and workplace throughout my life. I am here to welcome you, your family and friends to discover this wonderful place on Earth.”</p><p>“Whether your stay is short or long, tell us what matters to you and we can personalise your visit so that you make the most of your time with us.”</p><p class="signature">Antonio</p></div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
